1
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,400
Eunuch Jingyuan,

2
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:54,320
Eunuch Sun is dead.

3
00:00:58,120 --> 00:00:58,920
I know.

4
00:00:59,120 --> 00:00:59,920
You may leave.

5
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:00,480
Yes.

6
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:06,680
I didn't expect him to actually not disappoint me.

7
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:09,640
Are you okay?

8
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:12,170
It's good that you're okay.

9
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,539
They have all left.

10
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:17,970
Why are you still staying here?

11
00:01:20,039 --> 00:01:21,320
How is your injury?

12
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:24,039
What?

13
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,240
Did you want to see

14
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,640
if I would actually die?

15
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,360
You're in this state,

16
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:33,160
and you can still talk back to me.

17
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:46,200
After all that effort,

18
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,580
only Sun Liang was dealt with.

19
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,960
Sun Liang was loyal to her.

20
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,100
I didn't expect my aunt

21
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,720
to be so ruthless.

22
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,050
But that's fine.

23
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,170
After today,

24
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:05,880
we won't have to live under Sun Liang's surveillance.

25
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,440
What are you thinking about?

26
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:16,840
Nothing.

27
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,960
I just suddenly felt

28
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:21,600
that Chancellor Shen is quite cute.

29
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,240
That's true.

30
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,810
Then why did you drive him away?

31
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:30,040
He clearly cared about you just now.

32
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:33,440
Since ancient times, loyal officials often die.

33
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:36,440
Rather than staying by a tyrant's side and bearing a bad name,

34
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:38,370
it's better to remain uncorrupted

35
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,760
and keep the people safe.

36
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:44,840
Prime Minister Shen has served two emperors.

37
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,560
He is the current Left Prime Minister.

38
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:49,490
Si Xinglan must have thought about winning him over.

39
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,380
Are you afraid that

40
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:54,260
if Prime Minister Shen really works for you,

41
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:56,640
the Grand Princess won't tolerate him?

42
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,520
This is obviously a virtual game.

43
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,380
He is obviously a virtual character.

44
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,900
But at this moment,

45
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:10,240
I actually feel his sorrow and helplessness.

46
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:15,600
I just simply want to change the ending for one person.

47
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,120
Si Xingxuan,

48
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,280
have you ever thought about a question?

49
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,079
What?

50
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:24,410
To Prime Minister Shen,

51
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:27,040
the country comes before his family.

52
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:30,560
You always play the role of an incompetent ruler and alienate him.

53
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:33,079
He will only feel that the country is ruined,

54
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,440
and see no hope.

55
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,970
As a loyal minister,

56
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,079
he definitely hopes to be of use.

57
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,340
Shen Qingyan is full of pride.

58
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,760
It's good enough that he didn't help the Grand Princess

59
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:48,020
to eliminate the incompetent ruler and clean up the court.

60
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,620
In the whole court,

61
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:51,480
who doesn't want me dead?

62
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,050
Even if I am willing,

63
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,640
he wouldn't be willing to follow me.

64
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:58,920
But if you don't try,

65
00:03:58,920 --> 00:03:59,980
how would you know?

66
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:02,040
What if he is really willing to help you?

67
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,080
In time,

68
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:05,240
we can punch Prime Minister Zhou,

69
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,640
kick the Grand Princess,

70
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:09,440
and bring peace and prosperity back to Donglin.

71
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:15,920
The experiencer's character goal is 50% completed.

72
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,290
You two may step down first.

73
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,640
To think I was played by that brat.

74
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:47,540
Prime Minister Shen used to disdain His Majesty's absurd behavior the most.

75
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:48,960
Today,

76
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:52,240
he was actually willing to stay in His Majesty's bedchamber.

77
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:54,480
We cannot let him associate with Prime Minister Shen.

78
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,610
Doesn't he like pretending to be sick?

79
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:57,840
Then let him pretend.

80
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:58,880
In a few days,

81
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:01,080
our grand plan will be accomplished.

82
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:03,480
The Donglin empire will surely change hands.

83
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,320
A puppet without an heir,

84
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:07,450
let him jump around for a few more days.

85
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,720
Strangely enough,

86
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:13,900
whenever this kid is about to resort to violence...

87
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,960
As soon as he sees the fool,

88
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,250
he immediately calms down.

89
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,920
For so many years,

90
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,640
he actually forced himself

91
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,240
not to kill anyone.

92
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,280
This Si Xingxuan

93
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,640
is really not simple.

94
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:35,560
Since the Emperor cannot die right away,

95
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:39,560
isn't it easy for us to deal with that fool?

96
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:41,920
Now,

97
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,960
he is showing his fangs and wants to fight back.

98
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:48,090
Then we should strike where it hurts the most.

99
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,960
Zuoshan, you ran here to jump.

100
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,920
Sister Rong.

101
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,240
Why are you here?

102
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,640
I brought you a new toy.

103
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:05,840
Th-This is not a toy.

104
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:07,120
This is just a rock.

105
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,760
I'm not a fool.

106
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,840
This is no ordinary rock.

107
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:14,720
Ayan, put it in your bed to warm it up.

108
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,920
Once it's warm, it will turn into a puppy.

109
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,920
Turn into a puppy?

110
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,640
Turn into a puppy!

111
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,240
I... I want to try.

112
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:23,840
I'm so sorry, Little Prince.

113
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,720
Why isn't it changing yet?

114
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:28,240
A'yan can't warm it up alone.

115
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,440
Let me do it with you, okay?

116
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,280
So fast.

117
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:32,240
We need to turn it into a puppy.

118
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,440
A'yan.

119
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,520
How about we do this?

120
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,520
Oh, this is good.

121
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:51,000
I can't see it.

122
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,880
What are you doing?

123
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:01,040
Aunt, we are turning it into a puppy.

124
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,960
The little prince and I are truly in love.

125
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,120
Please grant us your blessing, Your Highness.

126
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,050
Change quickly, turn into a puppy.

127
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,240
A'yan.

128
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:11,880
How about

129
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,300
we go somewhere else to make puppies?

130
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,200
In my palace,

131
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:19,640
there are many puppies made of stones.

132
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,360
Go play at my place.

133
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,320
Oh, okay.

134
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:24,320
I want to make more puppies.

135
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,780
Escort the little prince.

136
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:26,440
Hurry.

137
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,720
Don't let the puppy get away.

138
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,880
Slow down.

139
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,440
You all saw it.

140
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:36,890
This is a royal forbidden area.

141
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:39,480
How dare these two commit such treason.

142
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,040
Even royal descendants,

143
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:44,240
if they damage the royal dignity,

144
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,200
must be punished with death.

145
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,880
This is the dignity of Donglin.

146
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,360
Yuanyuan.

147
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,920
I want to go see the puppy.

148
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,980
What are you doing?

149
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,360
How dare you touch the Little Prince?

150
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,080
Then can I touch him?

151
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,840
Where are you taking the Little Prince, Your Highness?

152
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,240
About where I take someone,

153
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:06,040
since when do I need to report to a servant like you?

154
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,360
Get out of my way.

155
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,160
I'll go see the dog first.

156
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,640
I'll play with you later.

157
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:43,400
Players cannot forcibly intervene in the main plot.

158
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:47,280
Designated characters can only act according to the game settings.
